For 15+ years, I have worked as a Business & Technology Solutions Consultant and Product Manager, specializing in strategic planning, IT, software development, Artificial Intelligence integration, and product prototyping.
</p> <p class="body-copy" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>
From requirements definition and scoping to delivery, release, and analytics, I lead cross-functional teams to build high-performance web/app experiences and AI automation pipelines.
</p> </div> </div> <div class="about-info-right--awards hide-mobile" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp> <h3 data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>Languages</h3> <ul data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp> <li data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>• Arabic: Mother Tongue</li> <li data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>• English: Expert</li> <li data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>• Persian: Expert</li> </ul> <h3 style="margin-top: 15px;" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>Additional Info</h3> <ul data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp> <li data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>• Experience: 15+ years</li> <li data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>• Working hours: 39,000+</li> <li data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>• Awards: 3 professional awards</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <div class="about-info-box-bottom" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp> <div class="awards-ticker" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp style="border-left: none;"> <div class="awards-ticker-track" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp> <div class="awards-ticker-group" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>15+ Years Experience</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>39,000+ Working Hours</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>+50% Web Traffic Growth</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>+35% Leads Growth</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>+45% Social Engagement</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>Afya Model MOA AI</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>Afya Model xiix ai LLM</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>1st Place National Project</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>2nd Highest CS Grade</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>~30% Operational Savings</div> <div class="awards-ticker-group-item glow-text" data-astro-cid-bb2dh2qp>Shalehi App Delivery</div> <d